
This are the steps to deploy the scripts

- All the dependencies needed for the scripts are available in anaconda python
  You can get that from here https://www.anaconda.com/download 
  The link will take you the page that suits your OS, download python3.6 from here

-Downlaod the  'workday_coding_test' folder from the google drive link provided

- Go to  'workday_coding_test' folder and run the script calc_wfreq.py like this:
  python calc_wfreq.py -pid <page_id> -n <How many top n words needed>
  ex: python calc_wfreq.py -pid 21721040 -n 3

- Run the command py.test inside the 'workday_coding_test' folder  to run the unit tests

